<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style/userpage.css">
</head>
<body>

  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm bg-body-tertiary rounded"  aria-label="Thirteenth navbar example">
    <div class="container-fluid">
      <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#special" aria-controls="special" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
        <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
      </button>
  
      <div class="collapse navbar-collapse d-lg-flex" id="special">
        <a class="navbar-brand col-lg-3 me-0" href="#" id="brand"><i>Aurora</i></a>
        <ul class="navbar-nav col-lg-6 justify-content-lg-center">
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="#" id="homebtn">Home</a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link borrowHistory" href="#" >Borrowing History</a>
          </li>
          
          <li class="nav-item dropdown">
            <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" href="#" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false">Books</a>
            <ul class="dropdown-menu">
              <li><a class="dropdown-item borrowBook" href="#">Borrow Book</a></li>
              <li><a class="dropdown-item returnBook" href="#">Return Book</a></li>
              <li><a class="dropdown-item currentLoans" href="#">Current Loans</a></li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="d-lg-flex col-lg-2 justify-content-lg-end">
          <ul class="navbar-nav col-lg-6 justify-content-lg-center">
            <li class="nav-item dropdown">
              <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" href="#" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false"><%=name%><br><%=id%></a>
              <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/account" id="accountbtn">Account</a></li>
                <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#" id="logOutBtn">Log Out</a></li>
              </ul>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="p-5  bg-body-tertiary rounded-3 " >
      <div class="container py-5">
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold" >ALL BOOKS</h1>
        <p class="col-md-12 fs-4">Discover a unique collection of books spanning literature, science, art, and history. Dive into a world of knowledge and inspiration, curated for every passionate reader.  </p>
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" type="button" id="allBooks">List All Books</button>
      </div>

      <div class="container py-5 ">
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold ">Borrow Book</h1>
        <p class="col-md-12 fs-4">Unlock the door to endless possibilities by borrowing a book from our vast collection. Whether you seek thrilling adventures, profound knowledge, or timeless classics, our library offers a treasure trove of stories waiting to be explored. Start your journey today and let every page take you somewhere new.   </p>
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg borrowBook" type="button">Borrow</button>
      </div>

      <div class="container py-5 ">
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold ">Return Book</h1>
        <p class="col-md-12 fs-4">Every book holds a story, and every journey must come full circle. Returning your book ensures that others can embark on the same adventure you once did. Keep the cycle of knowledge alive—return your book on time and help fellow readers discover the magic within its pages.   </p>
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg returnBook" type="button">Return</button>
      </div>

      <div class="container py-5 ">
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold ">Current Loans</h1>
        <p class="col-md-12 fs-4"> Keep track of your literary adventures with your current loans. Whether you're immersed in a thrilling mystery, exploring new worlds, or gaining valuable knowledge, these books are your companions on the journey of discovery. Remember to return them on time so others can embark on their own reading adventures.  </p>
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg currentLoans" type="button">Show Loans</button>
      </div>


      <div class="container py-5 ">
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold ">Borrowing History</h1>
        <p class="col-md-12 fs-4"> Your borrowing history is a reflection of your literary journey—each book a chapter in your adventure. Revisit the stories that shaped your imagination, the knowledge that expanded your horizons, and the worlds you once explored. Keep track of your past reads and let them inspire your next discovery.  </p>
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg borrowHistory" type="button" >Show Borrowing History</button>
      </div>


      <div class="container py-5 ">
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold ">Request Or Suggestion</h1>
        <p class="col-md-12 fs-4"> Have a book in mind that you'd love to see in our collection? Or a suggestion to enhance your library experience? Your voice matters! Share your requests and ideas with us, and help shape a library that caters to every reader’s needs.  </p>
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg request" type="button">Help Us</button>
      </div>


      

    </div>
  

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <script src="/script/dropdown.js"></script>
</body>
</html>